=head1 NAME

eris -- simple, easy-to-use Nix binary cache

=head1 SYNOPSIS

B<eris> [I<options>]... <[I<device options>] devices>...

=head1 DESCRIPTION

B<eris> is a simple, easy to use nix binary cache, that exports your Nix store
over HTTP.

=head1 CONFIGURATION

Lorem ipsum...

=head1 COMMAND LINE OPTIONS

Eris uses the Mojolicious L<hypnotoad(8)> server for deployment, and by default
exports several options to control Hypnotoad startup.

=over

=item B<-f>

Start in the foreground, as opposed to forking a daemon process.

=back

